snippet.title: Disney Sends Lawyers To DEFEND Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard In Lawsuit
snippet.description:
Disney Sends Lawyers To DEFEND Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard In Lawsuit
The current case between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard is ironically not one about money (for the most part) or property, it’s about character. In this particular case, the “character” of either Johnny Depp or Amber Heard. throughout their marriage (which lasted only a year). Now, each new development just deepens the rabbit hole.
